ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOperational Service Medal & Regulations
PrecisOrder directing that Letters Patent do issue instituting and creating an award in Canada designated and styled as the OPERATIONAL SERVICE MEDAL, whose description and eligibility requirements are set out in the OPERATIONAL SERVICE MEDAL REGULATIONS annexed to the Letters Patent.
